---
import Section from "../Section.astro";
---

<Section id="services" className="w-full">
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-2xl flex-col items-center justify-center gap-48 overflow-x-hidden bg-[#121212] py-20 md:py-36"
  >
    <div
      class="flex w-full flex-col justify-between gap-10 overflow-x-hidden px-10 md:flex-row"
    >
      <div class="w-full text-center sm:text-left md:w-[60%]">
        <h2 class="font-audiowide text-2xl font-semibold uppercase md:text-3xl">
          What I can do
        </h2>

        <h3 class="pt-5 text-white/70">You name it. I give it.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-xl md:text-2xl">
        <p>Figma designs</p>
        <p>Scalable Architectures</p>
        <p>Backend Development</p>
        <p>Frontend Development</p>
        <p>Search Engine Optimization</p>
        <p>Mail Campaigns + Landing Pages</p>
        <p>Chrome Extensions</p>
        <p>E Commerce</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex w-full flex-col justify-between gap-10 overflow-x-hidden px-10 md:flex-row"
    >
      <div
        class="flex w-full flex-col justify-between text-center md:w-[60%] md:text-left"
      >
        <h2 class="font-audiowide text-2xl font-semibold uppercase md:text-3xl">
          What my friends can do
        </h2>

        <div class="">
          <p class="pt-5 text-white/70">
            I said, you name it. I give it. Sometimes I could not.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-5 text-white/70">
            Which is why I made this section dedicated to my friends, you name
            it. we give it.
          </p>
          <p class="w-full pt-5 font-medium md:max-w-[55%]">
            Throughout the years of collaborating with clients, I've built a
            network of high-performance individuals ready to help us if needed.
          </p>
          <p class="w-full pt-5 font-medium md:max-w-[55%]">
            Once we start working together, I can intro you, or I can arrange
            the entire collaboration myself, so that you won't have to lift a
            finger.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-xl md:text-2xl">
        <p>Pretty much everything that I do, and</p>
        <p>IOS Apps</p>
        <p>Mobile Apps</p>
        <p>PWA, etc</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
